Package com.cafean.client.ui.beans

Class ModelEnumerationEditor

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.beans.PropertyEditorSupport
      • com.cafean.client.ui.beans.ModelEnumerationEditor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComponentDependent, ModelDependent, TargetDependent, IntrospectingEditor, OptionalPropertyEditor, java.awt.event.ItemListener, java.beans.PropertyEditor, java.util.EventListener
    public class ModelEnumerationEditor
extends java.beans.PropertyEditorSupport
implements java.awt.event.ItemListener, TargetDependent, IntrospectingEditor, OptionalPropertyEditor
    This bean editor contains a JComboBox for selecting between enumeration values.
